<lb n="0776b26" ed="T"/>五</note><note n="0776006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">脯＝晡【元】【明】</note><note n="0776006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">脯【大】，晡【元】【明】</note><app n="0776006"><lem wit="【大】">脯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">晡</rdg></app>利婆簸囉呵梨<note place="inline">十六</note>阿知多佛陀<note place="inline">十七</note>阿
